===Etymology===
{{liushu|p}} – a man bowing over to the left. Significantly abstracted – the middle cross was initially the knee, the stroke at bottom left was the bowed head, and the top was the back-swept hands or clothes.

===Han character===
{{Han char|rn=83|rad=氏|as=00|sn=4|four=7274<sub>0</sub>|canj=竹女心 (HVP)}}

# [[clan]], [[family]]
